Bengali is spoken by about 270 million people in the
Indian state of West Bengal and in People's Republic of
Bangladesh. This is an extra collection of Bengali fonts
for Slackware Linux.

To install the fonts in the contrib folder run the
slackbuild as CONTRIB=YES ./fonts-bengali-extra.SlackBuild

NOTE:
This package conflicts with the google-fonts package

This package contains the following fonts:
1. Akaash
2. Anek Bangla
3. Atma
4. BalooDa2
5. Chata
6. Galada
7. Hind Siliguri
8. Kalaa
9. Kalponik
10. Kalpurush
11. Lalsaluk
12. Mina
13. AdorshoLipi
14. AponaLohit
15. Bangla
16. BenSen
17. Sagar
18. SolaimanLipi
19. Sabala
20. Sapa
21. Siha
22. Siyam Rupali
23. Tiro Bangla
24. Nikosh
25. NikoshBAN
26. NikoshGrameen
27. NikoshLight
28. NikoshLightBAN
29. BenSen Handwriting
